page.title: 15ROADS, HAMPTON WICK
page.content: Many of the roads in{Hampton Wick} area are mainly residential and fairly quiet, apart from the busy Kingston Road. The houses are mainly detached or semi-deatched and have small gardens. Some houses have the River Thames at the end of the garden and some even have a boat moored on the river. Some of the roads are tree lined. All of them have street lights and cars are often parked along the sides of the road. Close by in most of the roads there is usually a pillar box and a telephone box.
